Data is everywhere. Data is essential to our customers. We need their data in our systems. That’s where you come in. We are currently seeking an ETL developer to design and implement ETL processes to inject customer data into our Products. You will leverage your ETL expertise to feed data from heterogeneous sources into our systems. You will use your well-polished business and communication skills to work with customers to understand their data requirements, help them make data-related decisions using your ETL knowledge and experience, and ultimately transition their application data to AbacusNext systems.
